summary: HC Gus or Libby because the AM redheads (not just these two) deserve eberything they've been put through.
question: HC Gus or Libby because the AM redheads (not just these two) deserve eberything they've been put through.
answer:
yeees (lets do both, shall we?)

Gus (my MAIN. MAN.)

  • that boy is a trombonist
  • probably has had like….. 50 broken arms
  • wears sunhats to the beach
  • one time he needed tutoring for a section in math so their teacher chose Cyrus to tutor him and TJ was like “am I jealous?? why… why would I be jealous??? It’s Gus… why… wHY AM I JEALOUS-“ (it was a very confusing moment for Teej”
  • Besides that he’s good at school (B’s)
  • s w i m t e a m
  • used to have a huge crush on buffy but just observed from a far and was WAY too awkward to actually talk to her
  • mamas boi
  • gus x campbells soup is OTP

Libby (im honestly in love w/ her and she’s not even real but that’s fine)

  • taught herself how to read and write Spanish and French when she was bored
  • loves ALL forms of art (crafting, drawing, sculpting…) but her favorite is spray paint (bAD ASS)
  • neighbors with amber and tj and growing up their moms were close so they would hang out alot
  • (warnin: death) her mom died when she was in elementary school, so it’s just her and her dad
  • her dad got her a cat a couple years ago named noodle who’s also deaf (since the kippens got a cat at the same time, they were named together ;))
  • paints her wall when she’s bored Rapunzel style
  • Xjskkdkd thought: tj and amber drift away in middle school when they become mean, so as tj decides not to be a dick anymore he goes an apologizes to libby (amber does later too)
  • SUPER good at video games
  • Rekindles old game night with the kippens once they’re friends again, but this time with the whole squad

summary:
hot take of the day: andi mack x shane dawson and friends
cyrus’ favorite is shane himself. he loves his conspiracy theory...
body:
hot take of the day: andi mack x shane dawson and friends

cyrus’ favorite is shane himself. he loves his conspiracy theory videos, and he loves all the dramatic series’. he admire’s how shane came from nothing and built basically his own empire.

tj’s favorite is drew. he loves his playful sense of humor and sometimes he secretly wishes he could grow his hair out to look like drew’s.

buffy’s favorite is ryland. she loves him mostly because he’s the more sane one of the group. she loves his relationship with his family, especially with his sister.

andi’s favorite is andrew. she loves him because he’s usually the more soft one of the group, and she always listens for his laugh in the background of the videos.

jonah’s favorite is garrett. he loves how he’s the crazy one of the group and he tends to like weird things that none of the rest of his friends do, which jonah relates to with frisbee.

amber’s favorite is morgan. she loves how she’s very relatable to everyone and not afraid to be herself. amber also thinks she’s gorgeous and would definitely melt on the spot upon meeting her.

please add on!! i didn’t really think this through too much so please add your thoughts and add other characters if you’d like :)
